data.description: Snug in the heart of up and coming Sharswood, this duplex offers a 2 Bedroom first level unit and a 4BR unit the two floors above.   Update the flooring, paint and fix a couple drywall ceilings and you have yourself a golden goose making you money.   As you enter the building, you are met by a beautiful sturdy wood stair case leading up to the 4BR and flanked to the right is the entry into the 2BR.  The living room is light an airy and flows into an L-shaped kitchen with nice wooden cabinets, tile floors and tile counters.  Down the hall is an amply-sized hall bath between two bedrooms, the rear bedroom being on the bigger side.  Off the rear bedroom is a nice-sized backyard.  Laundry is in the basement.  Upstairs you will find the 4BR unit.  Off the entry door to your right you are met by another L shaped kitchen with nice wood cabinets and tile counters.  Towards the front of the house is a spacious living room.  Down the hall towards the back of the house are two bedrooms with a hall bath.  Upstairs you will two more bedrooms with nice size, hall bath and laundry.    Minor upgrading is needed but this building is a sure money make close to public transportation and blocks away from Broad st. Owner has a month to month tenant downstairs 2 bedroom apt currently paying $850 monthly The 2&3rd floor is a 4 bedroom apt with 2 full baths. Owner was renting rooms to Local College students for $2000 monthly but also is great for a small family. all offers will be submitted to Owner. This neighborhood is rapidly on the up rise so don't miss out on this great money making property. Newer Heating system with Central air Laundry hookup inside both Apartments Gas Heat Electric Hot Water This Property is Priced Right. This is a As Is Condition.
